As a new player, we have a few suggestions: 

  Please read the <%^YELLOW%^faq%^RESET%^>, <%^YELLOW%^help newbie%^RESET%^>, and <%^YELLOW%^help rules%^RESET%^>. These should make things much easier for you.

  Read the posts on the main and announcement board to get a feel for what has been going on lately.

We are happy to have you here, enjoy yourself and always have fun.

